divs: Sighting Detailsi was filming in my back yard for birds i set my camera on a tripod and let it run on its own. for 1hour and when i played it back i cought a few different objects one object is on film at 11mins 14sec. one at 12mins 20sec. i was excited when i first saw it. the first object just popped onthe screen and than popped off at 11mins. 14sec. the next one flew in to view than backed up than flew forward at the sun as it turned out of the sunlight it went up out of sight
Summary: i was tring to video birds and cought somthing else
